            <h2>About Me</h2>
            <p>Welcome to my personal webpage! I am passionate about quality management and process improvement in luxury brands retail shop fitters and boutique construction. With 8 years of experience, including 3 years in India and 5 years in Dubai, I have worked on projects for renowned brands such as Loreal, Estee Lauder, Tomford, NARS, Valentino, Lancome, YSL, Prada, Armani, Hublot, Vacheron, and others.</p>
            <p>My roles have involved overseeing quality assurance processes, implementing quality control policies, conducting compliance audits, managing supplier quality, and driving process improvements. I have a degree in Mechanical Engineering from Anna University (2012-2016) and have been involved in various aspects of quality assurance management, including documentation, training, defect analysis, and QC inspections.</p>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2>Experience and Responsibilities</h2>
            <h3>Quality Assurance Management:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Oversee the entire quality assurance process for store projects.</li>
                <li>Develop and implement quality control policies and procedures.</li>
            </ul>
            <h3>Compliance Auditing:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Review processes and materials to ensure compliance with industry regulations and brand standards.</li>
                <li>Conduct regular audits on documentation compliance status.</li>
                <li>Assist in yearly ISO audits.</li>
            </ul>
            <h3>Supplier Quality Management:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Evaluate and manage supplier performance to ensure materials meet quality standards.</li>
                <li>Resolve quality issues with suppliers and improve supply quality.</li>
            </ul>
            <h3>Process Improvement:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Analyze quality control processes and identify areas for improvement.</li>
                <li>Implement corrective actions and preventative measures.</li>
            </ul>
            <h3>Documentation and Reporting:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Maintain detailed records of quality control processes and inspections.</li>
                <li>Prepare comprehensive reports on quality metrics and trends.</li>
            </ul>
            <h3>Training and Development:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Develop and deliver training programs on quality standards.</li>
                <li>Ensure team adherence to quality control protocols.</li>
            </ul>
